              mesopic and scotopic sensitivity was associated with increasing
              thickness of the total retina and the RPEDC and a decrease of the
              ONL and the PR-segments (P < 0.001, respectively). Conclusions:
              Accumulation of sub-RPE material in patients with intermediate
              AMD is spatially associated to quantifiable structural
