               0.368). Given this discrepancy, the ratio of the AFS area
               fraction within/outside of RPE atrophy could be used to
               differentiate between STGD1 and AMD with 65.0\% sensitivity and
               92.3\% specificity. Conclusions: Using OCT-A, comparison of
